#: ../../content/soins/index.md:1
msgid "Care"
msgstr "Soins"

#: ../../content/soins/index.md:4
msgid ""
"The Resthome Care application — prescriptions, care plans, vital signs, "
"nursing notes and clinical registers for the medical follow-up of residents."
msgstr ""
"L'application Soins de Resthome — prescriptions, plans de soins, signes "
"vitaux, notes infirmières et registres cliniques pour le suivi médical des "
"résidents."

#: ../../content/soins/index.md:7
msgid ""
"The **Care** application brings together all **medical and nursing** follow-"
"up of residents: medication, care plans, vital signs, notes, and the "
"**clinical registers** (falls, wounds, pain, nutrition…). It is designed for"
" the daily work of the care staff."
msgstr ""
"L'application **Soins** rassemble tout le suivi **médical et infirmier** des"
" résidents : médication, plans de soins, signes vitaux, notes, et les "
"**registres cliniques** (chutes, plaies, douleur, nutrition…). Elle est "
"pensée pour le travail quotidien du personnel soignant."

#: ../../content/soins/index.md:12
msgid "The dashboard"
msgstr "Le tableau de bord"

#: ../../content/soins/index.md:14
msgid ""
"When you open it, the **dashboard** highlights what needs attention today: "
"care to carry out, points to watch, administrations to give. You start from "
"here for your round."
msgstr ""
"À l'ouverture, le **tableau de bord** met en avant ce qui demande attention "
"aujourd'hui : soins à réaliser, points de vigilance, administrations à "
"faire. Vous partez de là pour votre tournée."

#: ../../content/soins/index.md:18
msgid "What the application covers"
msgstr "Ce que couvre l'application"

#: ../../content/soins/index.md:20
msgid ""
"**Prescriptions and medication** — Medication catalogue, prescriptions, "
"administrations, batches and stock. → [Prescriptions](prescriptions.md)"
msgstr ""
"**Prescriptions et médicaments** — Catalogue de médicaments, prescriptions, "
"administrations, lots et stock. → [Prescriptions](prescriptions.md)"

#: ../../content/soins/index.md:21
msgid ""
"**Care plans and vital signs** — Care plans, planning of the day's care, "
"vital signs and trends, nursing notes. → [Care plans](plans-de-soins.md)"
msgstr ""
"**Plans de soins et signes vitaux** — Plans de soins, planning des soins du "
"jour, signes vitaux et tendances, notes infirmières. → [Plans de "
"soins](plans-de-soins.md)"

#: ../../content/soins/index.md:22
msgid ""
"**Clinical registers** — Falls, pressure ulcers (Braden), wounds, pain, "
"restraint, nutrition (MNA), continence, mobility, cognition. → "
"[Registers](registres.md)"
msgstr ""
"**Registres cliniques** — Chutes, escarres (Braden), plaies, douleur, "
"contention, nutrition (MNA), continence, mobilité, cognition. → "
"[Registres](registres.md)"

#: ../../content/soins/index.md:24
msgid "Main menus"
msgstr "Menus principaux"

#: ../../content/soins/index.md:26
msgid ""
"**Medical** — Katz, nursing notes, attention points, vital signs entry, care"
" planning, today's care, my assigned care, care plans, prescriptions, "
"administrations, hospitalisation."
msgstr ""
"**Medical** — Katz, notes infirmières, points d'attention, saisie des signes"
" vitaux, planning des soins, soins du jour, mes soins assignés, plans de "
"soins, prescriptions, administrations, hospitalisation."

#: ../../content/soins/index.md:29
msgid "**Registers** — the dedicated clinical registers."
msgstr "**Registres** — les registres cliniques dédiés."

#: ../../content/soins/index.md:30
msgid "**Stock** — medication batches, stock withdrawals."
msgstr "**Stock** — lots de médicaments, sorties de stock."

#: ../../content/soins/index.md:31
msgid ""
"**Configuration** — medication catalogue, pathologies (ICD-10), allergens, "
"drug interactions, SAM database."
msgstr ""
"**Configuration** — catalogue de médicaments, pathologies (CIM-10), "
"allergènes, interactions médicamenteuses, base SAM."

#: ../../content/soins/index.md:34
msgid "Separate but connected"
msgstr "Séparée mais reliée"

#: ../../content/soins/index.md:37
msgid ""
"The Care application is separate from billing, but **connected to the "
"residents**: a hospitalisation entered here appears, on the billing side, as"
" an [absence](../facturation/absences.md) that adjusts the allowance."
msgstr ""
"L'application Soins est distincte de la facturation, mais **reliée aux "
"résidents** : une hospitalisation saisie ici se retrouve, côté facturation, "
"en [absence](../facturation/absences.md) qui ajuste le forfait."

#: ../../content/soins/index.md:42
msgid "Going further"
msgstr "Pour aller plus loin"

